Portainer MCP Safe is an altered-source fork of Portainer MCP by Portainer.io.

Original upstream project and source:
https://github.com/portainer/portainer-mcp

Fork repository target:
https://github.com/Malaccamaxgit/portainer-mcp-safe

This distribution retains the upstream license text unchanged in LICENSE.

Fork-specific changes in this distribution include safe-mode behavior for stack
output redaction, proxy restrictions, and Docker MCP Toolkit packaging under
the docker/ subdirectory.
